# Vegetable Pho with Crispy Tofu

Based on [Love and Lemons](https://www.loveandlemons.com/easy-vegetarian-pho) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251206153744/https://www.loveandlemons.com/easy-vegetarian-pho/)) and [The Viet Vegan](https://thevietvegan.com/homemade-vegan-vietnamese-pho) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251013162403/https://thevietvegan.com/homemade-vegan-vietnamese-pho/))

